{"tid":2507133,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘樂感員工，態度惡過狗 (2)","createTime":"2021-04-27T21:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T08:41:38.000Z","uid":78856,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc70462ae06b3faafb5ba020fadcbda724aaa50","tid":2507133,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T21:36:53.000Z","msg":"原po: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2503134/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2503134/page/1</a><br />\n前幾日同個朋友去飲嘢，嗌咗一支水煙同埋杯cocktail 。 <br />\n咁一開頭都冇乜嘢，幫我哋整水煙個人態度都好好。<br />\n<br />\n啲水煙都幾好，但啲cocktail 就真係一般，仲要百幾蚊一杯。咁唔好飲都唔緊要啦。<br />\n<br />\n點知到個bartender 走埋嚟問我地杯嘢飲味道如何，咁我朋友都成日飲cocktail ，<br />\n朋友都直接有禮貌咁樣同個bartender 講話杯野嘅味道好似爭少少。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到個bartender 直接當面話 呢度唔啱我哋飲...<br />\n誇張嘅係佢要語帶諷刺咁同其他客講：「啱啱嗰枱話我杯野唔好飲喎」<br />\n之後又大大聲咁講酒吧工會啲人個個都話佢整嘅嘢好飲。<br />\n本身諗住樂感好似係黃店桔梗嘅姊妹店。去支持下<br />\n<br />\n但經過今次之後，真係唔會再去。"},{"pid":"743986ab771b5ec31bb3fc4cca0d515b38c37c1a","tid":2507133,"uid":78856,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T21:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb87bRg1UGJKreEMvGjS9cedWNmtuPYEAiXrGEw2L1rTY?filename=iQQ67Hg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQQ67Hg.png&h=8cfe249b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成班垃圾圍爐包庇個垃圾中六藝術家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ad37811e28f45247f4f91c228af396e0b984d6","tid":2507133,"uid":78856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T21:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmby3iHZfsER3Lf5C9z2qhbignRcL7ohPck12iCsvXEp6q?filename=kTgNR9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTgNR9k.png&h=48f37e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一堆老細開 想去就小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff60e37a041d3dbecfc958e5dc659048b2e5c16","tid":2507133,"uid":61082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0